{"tid":1633482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武和理一人讓一步 再次合一！","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:51:56.000Z","uid":26827,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"047ad35864c8eee5a6b481b55f6026c262af8326","tid":1633482,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"今晚8點18區開花 爆鐵不爆舖<br />\n<br />\n爆鐵唔影響國際輿論<br />\n好處:明日大三罷 令所有商家跪低 <br />\n反正開唔到舖 唔爆舖都無所謂<br />\n<br />\n人權法案都好重要 但係係長線<br />\n過到之後都有排先執行<br />\n短期一定要大三罷<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家一人讓一步<br />\n唔好比人分化<br />\n今晚爆鐵不爆舖<br />\n爆舖等人權法過左再算<br />\n依加對商家已有阻嚇作用<br />\n唔會有人敢表態支持政府<br />\n<br />\n大家要有獨立思考 唔好比狗帶風向<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"b565d48f4ebbf398d37fbe85e2f18bf439f60d2f","tid":1633482,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45626979dbcb17fc37ef439e88c81051f2bfc2a3","tid":1633482,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"816502b262918d371dc1b1f8fd18c8a23e4489b2","tid":1633482,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96c6ec079cb769531cae50a570989ead268ca499","tid":1633482,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\"